---
title: Saucy Tex-Mex Pork & Bean Burrito Bowl with Garlic Rice & Salsa
description: Tonight, put together a bountiful bowl full of Tex-Mex flavours! With pork mince, spiced beans, fresh salsa and fragrant rice, every bite of this
bright meal is as good as the next!
